revision.text: {{also|xue}} ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Xues}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Xue'' is the 9932<sup>nd</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 3248 individuals. ''Xue'' is most common among Asian/Pacific Islander (97.88%) individuals.
